Summary:
The player has agreed to help Hadrian address the United Colonies Cabinet in hopes of getting access to their old Terrormorph research. The player can attempt to convince them to - or advice them against - opening the Armistice Archives, the respository of knowledge from the Colony War. 

Just as the decision is coming down, Terrormorphs attack the city. The player and Hadrian have to protect the city from the Terrormorphs rampaging around the spaceport. Once they have, they can return to the President, who informs them they've decided to help the player access the information they requested from the Archives.
